  <Docs>
    <summary>Specifies electro-optical transfer function (EOTF/OETF) characteristics as defined by ITU-T H.273 (CICP).</summary>
    <remarks><format type="text/markdown"><![CDATA[
## Remarks

`SKColorspaceTransferFnCicp` enumerates the electro-optical transfer functions
(EOTF/OETF) defined by ITU-T H.273 (Coding-independent Code Points). These
values describe the gamma or tone-mapping curve of a color space and are used
together with <xref:SkiaSharp.SKColorspacePrimariesCicp> when creating a color
space via <xref:SkiaSharp.SKColorSpace.CreateCicp(SkiaSharp.SKColorspacePrimariesCicp,SkiaSharp.SKColorspaceTransferFnCicp)>.

## Examples

```csharp
var colorSpace = SKColorSpace.CreateCicp(
    SKColorspacePrimariesCicp.Rec2020,
    SKColorspaceTransferFnCicp.Pq);
```
]]></format></remarks>
  </Docs>
